Context: George Brown College offers a variety of programs. Users can search for programs using the program finder tool based on subject matter, academic centre, and credential. The Entry Advising team is available to answer questions about choosing a program, admission requirements, and application processes. Interested individuals can sign up to receive information about application deadlines, college news, events, tours, and more. Contact information: 416-415-2000, TTY: 1-877-515-5559, ask.george@georgebrown.ca. The college's social media hub can also be visited for additional information. Please note that the information on this website is subject to change without notice and students are responsible for verifying George Brown College fee requirements.
